abstract: Alastair Macaulay reviews performance by Suzanne Farrell Ballet at Kennedy Center in Washington.
snippet: The Suzanne Farrell Ballet performed all-Balanchine programs in Washington; on Oct. 19 it arrives at the Joyce Theater in New York.
